            "notes": "The deck revolves around utilizing ramp and landfall triggers to quickly build up mana and overwhelm the opponent with powerful creatures and spells. Lumra, Bellow of the Woods serves as the commander, providing additional mana and card advantage throughout the game. Cards like Primeval Titan, Green Sun's Zenith, and Finale of Devastation allow for fetching key creatures from the deck to further pressure the opponent. The deck also includes utility lands like Maze of Ith and Ghost Quarter to disrupt the opponent's game plan. By consistently ramping and playing threats efficiently, the deck aims to put the opponent on the back foot and close out the game before they have a chance to stabilize."
